{"tid":266478,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平機會不跟進游蕙禎「支那」言論    核突伯父蕭思江申司法覆核","createTime":"2017-06-01T13:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T13:54:33.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eba9a24525d623ed8321dd6fc5e25978f80d4154","tid":266478,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T13:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/ws/660/amz/worldservice/live/assets/images/2016/10/12/161012055858_cn_hongkong_legco_oath_02_976x549_reuters_nocredit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fws%2F660%2Famz%2Fworldservice%2Flive%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F2016%2F10%2F12%2F161012055858_cn_hongkong_legco_oath_02_976x549_reuters_nocredit.jpg&h=b5a456a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由蕭思江出任主席的港人民權民生黨今日向高院提司法覆核，指青年新政的游蕙禎於立法會宣誓時用「refucking Chi Na」字詞，是對中國或中國人侮辱的用詞，但平機會決定不跟進事件，認為有關決定是越權及未履行責任，要求法庭下令平機會重新考慮，如維持原來決定則須公開原因。<br />\n<br />\n港人民權民生黨將平機會與游蕙禎列為答辯人，並將梁頌恆列為與訴訟有關係人士。申請人指有關字詞是對中國或中國人侮辱的用詞，是對本港中國人不受歡迎的行為，平機會應按種族歧視條例盡力調查到底，但平機會未有受理一班愛國人士的投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20120816/large/16lp2p6n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20120816%2Flarge%2F16lp2p6n.jpg&h=1a9c9d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以「飯碗舞」聞名嘅蕭思江，今屆就轉戰體育、演藝、文化及出版界，蕭思江話，佢喺特首選舉時已全力支持梁振英，及後獲梁振英覆信致謝，所以日後佢向政府提出合理訴求時，必獲支持喎，你信唔信？"},{"pid":"bbbda3de80cb90374e92eaf647191703245b9ac0","tid":266478,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T13:18:50.000Z","msg":"蕭思江\t獨立\t律師\t64\tM\t灣仔區 - 樂活 (B09)\t141 票 (5.8% 敗)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://54.178.169.73:8000/static/generated/dc2015/B09_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F54.178.169.73%3A8000%2Fstatic%2Fgenerated%2Fdc2015%2FB09_2.jpg&h=61bbb11e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=